3.20	Charles_Chukwuma_Soludo	Charles Chukwuma Soludo	Charles Chukwuma Soludo, CFR (born 28 July 1960) is a Nigerian economics professor and the immediate past Governor and Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN). He was named Governor on 29 May 2004. He is also a member of the British Department for International Development's International Advisory Group.	
